name: Top Test Prep
overview:
Top Test Prep (Company) provides private tutors, test prep, and admissions counseling programs to help students get into the best private schools, colleges and graduate schools.

Ivy League inspired company that provides highly-rated, private tutoring, admissions and application assistance for private school admissions (SSAT, ISEE, HSPT), college admissions (SAT, ACT) and grad school admissions (MCAT, GMAT, LSAT)

Our test prep and tutoring programs offer both objective and subjective improvements for student scores with comprehensive study plans, test prep books, and diagnostic exams.

Additionally, Top Test Prep complements our private tutoring programs with subjective help from admissions counselors – experts in respective fields such as admissions interviews, essay prep, and admissions application feedback and reviews. Top Test Prep has locations and private tutoring / test prep in the following cities: Alexandria, VA, Austin, Arlington, VA, Atlanta, Bethesda, Bridgeport-Stamford-Norwalk, Conn., Boston, Chicago, Cherry Hill, Dallas Ft. Worth, Fairfax, VA, Greenwich, CT, Los Angeles, McLean, VA, New York City, Philadelphia, Potomac, MD, Princeton, NJ, Providence, RI, San Diego, San Francisco, St. Louis, and Washington DC. We are now more than 25 cities strong with growing locations and outreach to more local communities.

Top Test Prep also has international tutoring programs in 10 different cities including Beijing, Dubai, Hong Kong, London, Paris, Seoul, Singapore, Sydney and Taipei.
